<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Prescription Approved - MetabolixMD</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      color: #2d2d2d;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    h1 {
      color: #2d6a4f;
    }
    a {
      color: #2d6a4f;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .logo {
      margin-top: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .logo img {
      width: 100px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Thank You for Choosing MetabolixMD</h1>
    <p>Dear <%= name %>,</p>
    <p>This email is to confirm your upcoming telehealth consultation. Please find the meeting details below:</p>
    <p><strong>Meeting Date Time:</strong> <%= meetTime %></p>
    <p><strong>Meeting Link:</strong> <a href="<%= meetLink %>" style="color: #4CAF50;">Join the Meeting</a></p>
    <p>Our expert consultant will assist you during the session, providing personalized guidance and support in accordance with telehealth guidelines. Please ensure you are in a quiet and private space with a stable internet connection for the best consultation experience.</p>
    <h3>How to Prepare for the Meeting:</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>Test your device and internet connection beforehand.</li>
        <li>Have your medical records or questions ready for discussion.</li>
        <li>Click the meeting link a few minutes before the scheduled time.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>If you have any questions or require assistance before the meeting, feel free to contact us at <a href="mailto:consultant@metabolixmd.com" style="color: #4CAF50;">consultant@metabolixmd.com</a>.</p>
    <p>We look forward to serving you and helping you on your health journey.</p>
    <p>Best regards,</p>
    <p><strong>The MetabolixMD Team</strong></p>
    <p style="font-size: 0.9em; color: #777;">We Care for Your Health</p>
  
    <div class="logo">
      <img src="/image/3.png" alt="MetabolixMD Logo">
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
